  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to study the effect of adjuvant or immediate hormonal therapy,
      versus placebo, in subjects who have either undergone a primary therapy (principally radical
      prostatectomy or radiotherapy) or who were otherwise to be managed by watchful waiting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
